PrecisAppointment of THERESA TAM of Ottawa, Ontario, to be Interim Chief Public Health Officer, Public Health Agency of Canada, to hold office during pleasure for a term of one year or until such time as a Chief Public Health Officer is appointed, whichever occurs first, effective December 17, 2016.
